gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 136, Nets 120
gameRecap.excerpt: Kevin Durant recorded 33 points, 5 rebounds and 8 assists in his return to Brooklyn, as the Suns defeated the Nets, 136-120. Jusuf Nurkic (28 points, 11 rebounds, six assists) and Devin Booker (22 points, eight assists, four 3PM) added a combined 50 points for the Suns in the victory. Cam Thomas tallied 25 points and four assists for the Nets in the losing effort. The Suns improve to 28-20 on the season, while the Nets fall to 19-28.
